name: Titanium Gift Pack
description: Our Titanium Gift Pack includes Almond and Mineral Exfoliator, Orange and Lime Shaving Cleansing Mouse, Green Apple Toner, Eye Reviving Complex Cream and Daily Moisturiser.

name: Green Apple Toner / Orange & Lime Cleansing Shaving Mouse
description: Two of our most popular products in this special pack.

name: Green Apple Toner
description:
Green Apple Toner

Nourish and tone your skin with juicy green apples dripping with vitamins and nutrition. Skin will be hydrated and firmed, active herbs purify the skin and provide supreme antioxidant benefits. 

Directions for use: Use after cleanser, masque or exfoliating cream to remove all traces of previous products and to reveal the clearness of the complexion. Apply to a dampened cotton pad to face and neck areas and leave on.

Ingredients: aqua, organic citrus aurantifolia juice, ethyl alcohol, organic salvia officinalis leaf extract, organic trifolium pratense extract, organic echinacea purpurea extract, organic azadirachta indica seed extract, organic cymbopogon flexuosus extract, organic ocimum basilcum extract, organic mentha piperita leaf extract, gluconolactone, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate, fragrance

name: Shaving Cleanser Mouse
description:
Orange & Lime Cleansing / Shaving Mousse 
Cleanse your skin and shave at the same time with our ultimate daily cleansing and shaving solution.  This fast-acting gel formulation contains the amazing antibacterial properties of bitter orange & lime rich  in Vatamin C to loosen and remove dirt and grime leaving skin squeaky clean and thoroughly refreshed.

Directions for use: Wet the skin and a small amount of the mousse and massage into your skin with fingertips in a circular motion covering the face. Shave. Completely remove with a lukewarm face cloth and then finish with an application of toner and/or moisturiser.

Ingredients: aqua, decyl glucoside, sodium cocoamphoacetate, kosher vegetable glycerin, organic citrus aurantium bergamia oil, organic citrus aurantium dulcis oil, wild harvested honey, gluconolactone, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate, xanthan gum, fragrance, citric acid

name: Bamboo Strengthening Masque
description:
Bamboo and guava join forces in this light gel strengthening masque. Elasticity and hydration are returned to the skin with the strength of bamboo loaded with antioxidants, vitamins and proteins. When partnered with exotic cartenoid - rich guava, the result is strong, healthy skin. 
Directions for use: Apply a thin layer of masque with fingertips to cleansed skin, avoiding the eye area. Leave on for 5 minutes or longer. Gently massage into face and remove with a damp cloth or facial sponge.

name: Guava and Bamboo Cleanser
description:
Bamboo and guava join forces in this strengthening cleanser to return elasticity and hydration to the skin. The strength of bamboo, loaded with antioxidants, vitamins and proteins when partnered with exotic cartenoid-rich guava result in strong, healthy skin. 
Directions for use: Apply a small amount of the cleanser and massage into skin with fingertips in a circular motion covering the face and neck for 1-3 minutes. Completely remove with a lukewarm face cloth and then finish with an application of toner.

name: Eye Reviving Complex
description:
The skin around the eyes is much more sensitive than the skin on the rest of a person's face needing an eye cream which is effective but does not overload. This lightweight anti-aging eye cream is clinically proven to reduce the depth of wrinkles by increasing hydration. Restores moisture where it is needed most. 
Directions for use: Apply a thin layer to cleansed skin around the eyes as a moisturizer using your fourth finger with a gentle patting type motion.

name: Goji & Bamboo Moisturiser
description:
This lightweight moisturizer recharges and hydrates the skin. A unique blend of grape seed oil and coconut oil helps soothe shaved skin whilst grapefruit oil decongest and offer free-radical protection. Goji and bamboo restore the skinâ€™s elasticity, suppleness and essential nutrients.
Directions for use: Apply a thin layer to cleansed skin as a moisturizer.

name: Almond and Mineral Treatment
description:
This invigorating exfoliant will uncover gorgeous skin that feels soft and supple! Almond nourishes skin, ground ivy tones and tightens the skin, while paprika stimulates and oxygenates the skin, leaving a rosy complexion.
Directions for use: Apply a small amount and massage into skin with fingertips in a circular motion covering the face and neck for 1-3 minutes. Completely remove with a lukewarm face cloth and then finish with an application of toner and moisturizer.
